{"id":"abidan","term":"Abidan","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Father of judgment; judge, head of the tribe of Benjamin at the Exodus (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Numbers 1:11\">Num. 1:11</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Numbers 2:22\">2:22</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Numbers 1:11","Numbers 2:22"]}